refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:1:# mzPeak ground-truth schema (extracted from refs/mzPeak/small.unpacked.mzpeak)
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:3:Authoritative Arrow/Parquet schemas of a real mzPeak archive produced by the HUPO-PSI Rust
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:8:- `mzpeak_index.json` — `{ "files":[{name,entity_type,data_kind}], "metadata":{...} }`
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:9:- `spectra_metadata.parquet` — packed parallel tables (REQUIRED)
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:10:- `spectra_data.parquet` — point layout signal (REQUIRED)
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:11:- `spectra_peaks.parquet` — point layout centroids (OPTIONAL)
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:12:- `chromatograms_metadata.parquet` — (present when chromatograms exist)
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:18:## spectra_data.parquet / spectra_peaks.parquet (point layout)
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:21:point: struct<spectrum_index: uint64, mz: double, intensity: float>
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:24:m/z = float64, intensity = float32. One row per data point. mz sorted ascending per spectrum.
refs/_findings/mzpeak_groundtruth_schema.md:29:point: struct<chromatogram_index: uint64, time: double, intensity: float, ms_level: int64>
