.planning/phases/02-spectra-signal-data/02-01-PLAN.md:197:    - A centroid-only scan (not Profile, or no CentroidStream) contributes ONLY to spectra_data — never duplicated into spectra_peaks.
.planning/phases/02-spectra-signal-data/02-01-PLAN.md:198:    - A run with no qualifying scans writes no spectra_peaks and does not list it in mzpeak_index.json.
.planning/phases/02-spectra-signal-data/02-01-PLAN.md:199:    - When spectra_peaks is written, mzpeak_index.json files[] contains a spectra_peaks entry with data_kind "peaks"; when not, it does not.
