     9	- `spectra_metadata.parquet` — packed parallel tables (REQUIRED)
    10	- `spectra_data.parquet` — point layout signal (REQUIRED)
    11	- `spectra_peaks.parquet` — point layout centroids (OPTIONAL)
    12	- `chromatograms_metadata.parquet` — (present when chromatograms exist)
    13	- `chromatograms_data.parquet`
    14	
    15	Per-Parquet ZSTD internal compression. CV terms encoded as `NS:accession` CURIEs; column
    16	names embed the accession, e.g. `MS_1000511_ms_level`.
    17	
    18	## spectra_data.parquet / spectra_peaks.parquet (point layout)
    19	
    20	```
    21	point: struct<spectrum_index: uint64, mz: double, intensity: float>
